      'Maintained 200+ power tools and pneumatic equipment for 45-person construction crew, implementing weekly inspection program that reduced tool-related injuries by 55% and extended average tool life by 30%',
      'Trained 20 new hires on safe power tool operation including table saw, circular saw, and nail gun use per OSHA requirements, achieving 100% compliance on quarterly safety audits',
      'Transitioned 8-person framing crew from corded to Milwaukee M18 cordless platform, reducing setup time by 25% and eliminating trip hazard incidents from extension cords'
